{
  "stem": "5188.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was associated with the church, and there was religious instruction in the school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I and a few Evangelical-- or-- Protestant-- students, and there were just a few in this town where I went to school and lived-- the Protestant students and I were excused from the Catholic instruction.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we used to go out in the schoolyard and play.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was, however, one little catch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father had told the teacher that when they do the I should stay in, because it wouldn't hurt me to learn about the And actually, that was the beginning of my religious instruction.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did stay whenever they had the",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the religious instruction, I think was done-- we had a different teacher for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it must have been someone from the church, either the pastor or whoever they sent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did you get to school each day?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a short walk, maybe 15 minutes or so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we went to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We always had snack time around 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "School started at 8:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At 10 o'clock there was a 20 minute break.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we all ate a sandwich-- when the weather was nice-- in the schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we played for 20 minutes, and then went back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "School was over at noon, at 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we went home for dinner, for, you know, a good midday meal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was our warm meal of the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then on some days, I think once or twice a week, school was in the afternoon from 2 o'clock on-- from 2:00 to 4:00-- but not every day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the afternoon, the girls would learn how to do needlework.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You learned how to sew, how to crochet, how to knit, and do embroidery.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
